snippet.title: Village & Pillage: A Wanderous Journey
snippet.description:
A journey begins as a Wandering Trader sets out into the Overworld with a trusty llama. Will they find what they are searching for?

Part of the Village & Pillage update. Learn more about the Wandering Trader: http://www.minecraft.net/en-us/article/meet-wandering-trader
